          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1713265007679-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced onion</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and <strong>tomato wedges </strong>with your<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>ground coriander </strong>and a large pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Cook for, 2-3 min or until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1713265011028-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1713265011028-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1713265011028-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1713265011028-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1713265011028-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the <strong>peanut stock </strong>and the <strong>browned chicken </strong>to the pan</p><p>Cook, covered, for 8-10 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>Mozambican-style chicken & peanut stew</strong></p><p>Add most of the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>(save some for garnish!) and most of the <strong>chopped peanuts</strong> (save some for garnish!) to the <strong>cooked rice </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>coriander rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1713265014114-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1713265014114-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1713265014114-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1713265014114-x1000.jpg",
